          "parent": "",
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Reed Kanemaru earned a BS in Computer Science from University of California, Riverside in 2020 and an MS in Computer Science from University of California, Riverside in 2021. Since graduating, he has worked as a Content/Software Developer at zyBooks.",
          "dir": "ltr"
