      "blocks": [
        {
          "id": "p6-b1",
          "parent": "",
          "type": "figure",
          "caption": "A horizontal continuum graphic illustrating academic integrity practices categorized into three sections: Approved, Ask Instructor, and Not Approved. The 'Approved' section includes icons for 'Your Original Work' and 'Quoting & Crediting Another's Work'. The 'Ask Instructor' section features icons for 'Checking Your Answers Online', 'Group Work', 'Reusing Past Original Work', 'Sharing Answers', and 'Artificial Intelligence, Chatbot Apps'. The 'Not Approved' section includes icons for 'Posting Questions & Answers', 'Plagiarizing Work', and 'Getting Others To Do Your Work'.",
