          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "provide access to online streaming services include Spotipy (https://openstax.org/r/100spotipy), Pytube (https://openstax.org/r/100pytube), and Pydora (https://openstax.org/r/100pydora). Python-related tools often have the letters \"py\" in their name.",
