        },
        {
          "id": "p10-b16",
          "parent": "",
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "The print() function displays output to the user. Output is the information or result produced by a program. The sep and end options can be used to customize the output. Table 1.1 shows examples of sep and end.",
