      "blocks": [
        {
          "id": "p32-b1",
          "parent": "",
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "had been #1 for the previous 20 years.",
          "dir": "ltr"
        },
        {
          "id": "p32-b2",
          "parent": "",
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Another way to see Python's popularity is to analyze how frequently Python is discussed online. Stack Overflow (https://openstax.org/r/100overflow) is a question-and-answer website for programmers. Figure 1.3 shows the number of questions asked each month that were tagged with Python, JavaScript, and so forth. In recent years, Python has become the most asked about language in programming forums.",
